                 <span style="font-size:14px;">
                  <span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">
                   <span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                    <a data-content="http://www.lumbeetribe.com/single-post/2018/01/29/2018-Tribal-Council-Committees" data-type="external" href="http://www.lumbeetribe.com/single-post/2018/01/29/2018-Tribal-Council-Committees" rel="undefined" target="_blank">
